---
import MinimalLegalLayout from '../../layouts/MinimalLegalLayout.astro'
import { getBreadcrumbSchema } from '../../lib/seo'

const breadcrumbSchema = getBreadcrumbSchema([
  { name: 'Home', url: 'https://flexen.co/en/' },
  { name: 'Privacy Policy', url: 'https://flexen.co/en/privacy' },
])
---

<MinimalLegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Flexen UG"
  description="Privacy policy for Flexen UG (haftungsbeschränkt). Covers flexen.co and all products (Flexen, Project Pluto)."
  locale="en"
  canonicalPath="/en/privacy"
  schema={breadcrumbSchema}
>
  <section class="section min-h-screen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h1 font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary text-body mb-12">
          This privacy policy applies to <strong class="text-white">flexen.co</strong> and all
          products of Flexen UG (haftungsbeschr&auml;nkt) — currently
          <strong class="text-white">Flexen</strong> and
          <strong class="text-white">Project Pluto</strong>. In-app data processing is additionally
          governed by each product's in-app privacy notice.
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-invert text-secondary text-body space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">1. Controller</h2>
            <p>
              The controller for data processing on this website is:<br /><br />
              <strong class="text-white">Flexen UG (haftungsbeschr&auml;nkt)</strong><br />
              Paul-Heidelbach-Stra&szlig;e 14<br />
              34134 Kassel, Germany<br />
              Email: <a href="mailto:info@flexen.co" class="text-flexen-accent hover:underline"
                >info@flexen.co</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">2. Hosting</h2>
            <p>
              This website is hosted by Google Firebase Hosting (Google Ireland Limited, Gordon House, Barrow
              Street, Dublin 4, Ireland). When you visit the website, information (e.g. IP address, time of
              access, page requested, user agent) is automatically stored in server log files. This data is
              used solely for the purpose of stable website operation and cannot be attributed to specific
              individuals. The legal basis is Art.&nbsp;6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in stable website
              operation).
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">3. Contact by Email</h2>
            <p>
              When you contact us by email (e.g.
              <a href="mailto:info@flexen.co" class="text-flexen-accent hover:underline"
                >info@flexen.co</a
              >), we process the data you submit (email address, content, name if provided) for the purpose
              of handling your request. Legal basis is Art.&nbsp;6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in
              responding). The data is deleted as soon as it is no longer required for our response and no
              statutory retention obligations apply.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">4. Cookies and Tracking on this Website</h2>
            <p>
              This website sets <strong class="text-white">no cookies</strong> and uses
              <strong class="text-white">no tracking</strong>. No third-party scripts (e.g. Google Analytics,
              Facebook Pixel) are embedded.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">5. Analytics in the Flexen App (PostHog)</h2>
            <p>
              <em>This section concerns the Flexen mobile app, not this website.</em>
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              With your explicit consent, we use <strong class="text-white">PostHog</strong> (PostHog Inc., 2261 Market
              Street #4008, San Francisco, CA 94114, USA) in the Flexen mobile app to analyse usage. All processing
              takes place exclusively on EU servers in Frankfurt, Germany — your data never leaves the European Union.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              <strong class="text-white">Legal basis:</strong> Art.&nbsp;6(1)(a) GDPR (consent). You can withdraw your
              consent at any time in the app's settings under &ldquo;Anonymous usage statistics&rdquo;. This feature is
              <strong class="text-white">disabled by default</strong> on first use (opt-in).
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              <strong class="text-white">Purpose:</strong> Improving the app, detecting errors, understanding which features
              are used, measuring user retention.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4"><strong class="text-white">Data processed:</strong></p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
              <li>
                Event metadata (e.g. &ldquo;meal logged&rdquo;, &ldquo;workout completed&rdquo;),
                <strong class="text-white">without</strong> meal or workout content
              </li>
              <li>Screen views and tab switches</li>
              <li>Device and operating system information (model, OS version, language)</li>
              <li>
                Session replays: recordings of your screen interactions, with
                <strong class="text-white">all text and images automatically masked</strong>
              </li>
              <li>A pseudonymous user ID (Firebase UID) to associate events</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              <strong class="text-white">What we explicitly do NOT collect:</strong> the contents of your meals, chat
              messages with Julio, weight values, steps, sleep data or any other health parameters.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              <strong class="text-white">Retention:</strong> Event data for a maximum of 12 months, session replays for 30
              days.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              <strong class="text-white">Data processing agreement:</strong> We have a Data Processing Agreement (DPA) with
              PostHog pursuant to Art.&nbsp;28 GDPR. PostHog privacy policy: <a
                href="https://posthog.com/privacy"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                class="text-flexen-accent hover:underline">posthog.com/privacy</a
              >.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
              <li>Access your stored data (Art.&nbsp;15 GDPR)</li>
              <li>Rectification of inaccurate data (Art.&nbsp;16 GDPR)</li>
              <li>Erasure of your data (Art.&nbsp;17 GDPR)</li>
              <li>Restriction of processing (Art.&nbsp;18 GDPR)</li>
              <li>Data portability (Art.&nbsp;20 GDPR)</li>
              <li>Object to processing (Art.&nbsp;21 GDPR)</li>
              <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority (Art.&nbsp;77 GDPR)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              Contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@flexen.co" class="text-flexen-accent hover:underline"
                >info@flexen.co</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">7. External Links</h2>
            <p>
              This website links to the Apple App Store and Google Play Store. The respective privacy policies of
              Apple and Google apply to data processing by these services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">8. Fonts</h2>
            <p>
              This website uses locally hosted fonts (self-hosting). No connections to external font servers (e.g.
              Google Fonts) are established.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading mb-4 text-h3 font-bold text-white">9. Changes</h2>
            <p>
              We reserve the right to update this privacy policy to reflect changes in the legal landscape or in
              our services. The current version is always available on this page.<br /><br />
              Last updated: June 2026
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MinimalLegalLayout>
